data.description: Discover the perfect starter home at 217 Westmoreland Ave, where cozy charm meets thoughtful design. This well-maintained 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom home is ideal for those looking to embark on their homeownership journey. The interior welcomes you with a warm and inviting atmosphere, featuring spacious rooms. The kitchen is equipped with modern appliances, making meal prep a breeze. New metal roof in 2022.      This quaint home extends its appeal beyond the interior, with a level yard that requires minimal upkeep. The property is a testament to pride of ownership, ensuring a move-in-ready experience for its new owner!
